REPOSITORY
==========

This is a git repository containing multiple Portage trees that can be used by
Gentoo-compatible GNU/Linux distributions. To use this repository, you must
have git installed, or alternatively it can be browsed online at
http://github.com/funtoo/portage/tree/master.

BRANCHES
========

If you are browsing this repository at http://github.com/funtoo/portage/tree/master, 
you can view the contents of the repository by choosing a branch under the
"all branches" menu. This repository contains the following branches:

 * master           Contains this README file as well as licensing information

   gentoo.org       Contains an official Gentoo Linux Portage repository
    \ 
     funtoo.org     Contains an official Funtoo Portage repository

HOW TO USE
==========

Please consult our online documentation at
http://github.com/funtoo/portage/wikis for up-to-date, easy-to-use
documentation on how to use this repository for a variety of purposes.

